sources.description:
Zoombies: When a mysterious virus sweeps through a safari park, transforming the animals into undead predators, the remaining survivors must stop the outbreak before the infected creatures escape and wreak havoc on the entire city.
2016.  Stars: Ione Butler, Andrew Asper, LaLa Nestor

Zoombies 2: While arresting poachers in the jungle, a game ranger unexpectedly saves their lives when a horde of zombie animals launches a deadly attack. Now trapped and outnumbered, the ranger and poachers must form a tense alliance to survive and stop the undead creatures from spreading a super-zombie virus across the globe.
2019.  Stars: Erica Sturdefant, Jonathon Buckley, Jarrid Masse
